        "raw_body": "\n## First Bell\n\nThe chapter begins with a heading and a short paragraph about the frozen dock.\n\n:::section{title=\"Inner Yard\"}\n\nThe section continues the report while the nested container stays open.\n\n:::columns{count=2 gap=\"1.5rem\"}\n\n:::column\nThe left column describes the western approach, where lanterns hang every ten paces along the stone wall.\n:::\n\n:::column\nThe right column covers the eastern gate, still locked since the last inspection.\n:::\n\n:::/columns\n\n:::/section\n",
